Abstract = {The increasing use of social media brings with it several problems. The
   usage of insulting content on social networks, for some people or
   institutions, constitutes crimes. In this case, the study is about
   analyzing text content shared by users in the social media with the help
   of Naive Bayes Method and Vector Space Model from Machine Learning
   methods, and whether or not these shares contain insults, if any, and at
   what rate they contain.},
