   Guangdong Acad Bldg Res, Res Inst Road \& Bridge},
Abstract = {Through data processing of massive population crime, K-means mining
   algorithm is applied to the public security system. When dealing with
   large amount of data, K-means algorithm clustering results are greatly
   influenced by the choice of initial clustering center. If the selection
   of initial clustering center is improper, the clustering results may be
   trapped in local optimal solution, and get better clustering effect. So,
   adaptive genetic algorithm is used to optimize Kmeans algorithm. The
   experiment results show that the proposed scheme can get the valuable
   information and ideal clustering effect.},
