Abstract = {An Artificial Neural Networks (ANN) model identifying JWH Synthetic
   Cannabinoids, that we have developed based on a combination of
   topological, 3D-MoRSE (Molecule Representation of Structure based on
   Electron diffraction) and ADMET (Absorption, Distribution, Metabolism,
   Excretion and Toxicity) molecular descriptors, is described and
   analyzed. The validation results indicate that this computerized system
   has a very high potential for efficiently predicting the class
   membership of JWH and discriminating them from a large variety of
   (non-JWH) substances of forensic interest.},
