Organization = {Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Informat Engn; Deakin Univ; Beijing Jiaotong
   Univ, Sch Comp \& Informat Technol},
Abstract = {This paper proposes a new data security management and control platform
   to solve the problem that it lacks differentiated protection for the
   mass and heterogeneous data assets of enterprises, the data asset
   protection strategy is at a much coarse-grained level, and the
   enterprise security products are concerned only with their own protected
   equipment, lacking a unified security view, and unable to conduct big
   data tracking and forensics. First, it assigns the confidentiality,
   integrity and availability of data assets based on three characteristics
   of data security (confidentiality C, integrity I, usability A), to
   better reflect the business value of data assets, and it distinguishes
   the levels of data assets value, to improve the utilization of security
   protection tools. Then the platform automatically assigns specific data
   levels according to data classification, making fine-grained access
   control possible. It also studies the construction method of safety
   view, so as to effectively solve the problem that it lacks
   differentiated protection for corporate data assets, the data asset
   protection strategy is at a much coarse-grained level and lacks a
   unified security view, and unable to conduct big data tracking and
   forensics.},
