   Marinelli, Enrico; Zaami, Simona; Carlier, Jeremy, Sapienza Univ Rome, Unit Forens Toxicol, Sect Legal Med, Dept Anat Histol Forens \& Orthoped Sci, I-00198 Rome, Italy.},
